    "description": "The Ecommerce-buildTime API offers comprehensive services for managing products, user accounts, shopping carts, orders, payments, and shipping tracking within an e-commerce platform. It enables seamless operations such as adding products to carts, placing orders, processing payments, and tracking shipments to provide a complete end-to-end shopping experience.",
